data.description: Price reduced 10K!!!!Showings on Saturday and Sunday Only!!!!!. Welcome to this Amazing 1 year young 3 level, 4-bedroom, 3 full bathroom, 1 half bathroom Townhome with over 2350 sq. ft.in Gainesville. Features, 1Car Garage ,3 Upper-Level Bedrooms, Luxurious owner's suite w/ 2 walk in closets bedroom bath features a Spa-Shower. Lower lever 4th bedroom w/half bath that leads out to a fenced back yard…… could be converted to a den. Gleaming hardwood floors, huge gourmet kit w/ ss. appliances, white cabinets & center island. Large upstairs laundry room. Entry -level mud room built-in. Highly Sought After Subdivision with Wonderful Amenities and Perfect Location in Popular Gainesville.  Best of all, the Seller's Current VA Mortgage is Assumable at an extremely low 3.75% Interest Rate. *****An important thing to know about VA loans is that they are assumable. This means that a borrower can take over the terms of an existing VA loan, even if they are not eligible to take out a VA loan for themselves. With that, the home buyer will have the same mortgage payment the home seller had. The seller has a great interest rate locked in, the assumable nature******. Please inquire for more details. For Non-VA Qualified -VA Buyers, this is still an amazing property and is a definite must see!!!
